{"title":"唱支山歌献给党","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":12,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱支山歌献给党"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席来过五指山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔黎族新民歌〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席来过五指山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄树下歇过马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临走在树下洒瓢水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红艳艳地开满一树花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席来过五指山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古树野藤把路拦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他亲手辟开一条路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山南山北连一片。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金丝银丝连北京"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔藏族新民歌〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雅砻江水湾又湾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我家就在长包山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满山桑树排又排，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采回桑叶来喂蚕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"守更姑娘把蚕喂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蚕儿长得粗又肥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蚕儿吐银又吐金，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村村社社金银堆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千牛驮来万人背，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金丝银丝连北京。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔达斡尔族新民歌〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春季里来草发青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"达斡尔人民忙春耕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席好比春天雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能使万物得重生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏季里来好时光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里禾苗长的旺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席好比暖太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五谷生金浴阳光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋季里来丰收忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打下的粮食堆满仓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席好比是灯塔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指出集体大道明又亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬季里来北风吹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北风冷身不冷心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金碗里斟上高粱酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感谢毛主席大救星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在苗山望北京"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔苗族新民歌〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苗山高，苗山好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苗山遍地红旗飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在苗山望北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主席对我苗家笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主席对我苗家笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义光明道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土家苗汉一条心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民生活年年好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苗山好，苗山高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢乐鼓声阵阵敲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苗家跟着共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹浪打不动摇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放我可爱的故乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔高山族歌词〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台湾是个好地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台湾是我的故乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可恨那万恶的美帝国主"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"义野心狼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹂躏我的故乡，我的故乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台湾是个好地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台湾是我的故乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶走那万恶的美帝国主义野心狼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放我的故乡，我的故乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要我回头万不能"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔瑶族新民歌〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山高岭一蔸藤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藤子开花十二层，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今走上集体路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要我回头万不能。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}